# Title: UAC Bypass Using EventVwr
# Author: Antonio Cocomazzi (idea), Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-04-27
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the pattern of a UAC bypass using Windows Event Viewer
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.stealth
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_event/file_event_win_uac_bypass_eventvwr.yml

TargetFilename IN ("*\\Microsoft\\Event Viewer\\RecentViews", "*\\Microsoft\\EventV~1\\RecentViews") NOT (Image IN ("C:\\Windows\\System32\\*", "C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\*"))